    "body": "If `val = val.add(delta);` is replaced by `val = Math.add(val, delta);`, the estimator can find a finite value. \r\n\r\nMy suspicion is that the gas estimator cannot correctly resolve the jump destination because of the masking of the \"combined function entry label\".",
